title: Alawar Games - BubbleTown - Match3 Arcade [h33t][Wendy99]
description:
Bubble Town


Save Borb Bay from disaster in this addictive arcade-puzzler. 
One shot from the chute and you'll be hooked! Bubble Town will 
test your wits, not just your reflexes. Join the unforgettable 
cast of characters for an adventure of bubble-popping proportions. 
Just watch out for the Danger Zone! Choose from Journey Mode or 
Arcade Mode. The addictive gameplay will give you hours of fun!
